# Perfil core

- Read `AGENTS.md` before structural changes.
- Types live in `src/types/<domain>.ts`; re-export from `src/types/index.ts`.
- After editing `src/lib/`, run `npm test`.
- No React in content scripts. No secrets in content scripts.
- Use `tab-bridge.sendTabMessage` for background → tab communication.
